{"html":"<h2>Tactic(s)</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: functional<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: C<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;AgSt_S7&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;AgSt&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;~skD&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;~skS&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: message_authentication<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: s<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;AgSt_S11\\(&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;~rS&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;~rD&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;!KU\\(~vc&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;!HK\\(&#39;Human&#39;,&#39;vc&#39;,~vc&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;InitK\\(&#39;Human&#39;,&#39;m&#39;,&quot;</p><br/>\n","title":"Tactics"}